002package com.commercetools.api.predicates.query.common;
003
004import java.util.function.Function;
005
006import com.commercetools.api.predicates.query.*;
007
008public class ClientLoggingQueryBuilderDsl {
009    public ClientLoggingQueryBuilderDsl() {
010    }
011
012    public static ClientLoggingQueryBuilderDsl of() {
013        return new ClientLoggingQueryBuilderDsl();
014    }
015
016    public StringComparisonPredicateBuilder<ClientLoggingQueryBuilderDsl> clientId() {
017        return new StringComparisonPredicateBuilder<>(
018            BinaryQueryPredicate.of().left(new ConstantQueryPredicate("clientId")),
019            p -> new CombinationQueryPredicate<>(p, ClientLoggingQueryBuilderDsl::of));
020    }
021
022    public StringComparisonPredicateBuilder<ClientLoggingQueryBuilderDsl> externalUserId() {
023        return new StringComparisonPredicateBuilder<>(
024            BinaryQueryPredicate.of().left(new ConstantQueryPredicate("externalUserId")),
025            p -> new CombinationQueryPredicate<>(p, ClientLoggingQueryBuilderDsl::of));
026    }
027
028    public CombinationQueryPredicate<ClientLoggingQueryBuilderDsl> customer(
029            Function<com.commercetools.api.predicates.query.customer.CustomerReferenceQueryBuilderDsl, CombinationQueryPredicate<com.commercetools.api.predicates.query.customer.CustomerReferenceQueryBuilderDsl>> fn) {
030        return new CombinationQueryPredicate<>(
031            ContainerQueryPredicate.of()
032                    .parent(ConstantQueryPredicate.of().constant("customer"))
033                    .inner(fn.apply(
034                        com.commercetools.api.predicates.query.customer.CustomerReferenceQueryBuilderDsl.of())),
035            ClientLoggingQueryBuilderDsl::of);
036    }
037
038    public StringComparisonPredicateBuilder<ClientLoggingQueryBuilderDsl> anonymousId() {
039        return new StringComparisonPredicateBuilder<>(
040            BinaryQueryPredicate.of().left(new ConstantQueryPredicate("anonymousId")),
041            p -> new CombinationQueryPredicate<>(p, ClientLoggingQueryBuilderDsl::of));
042    }
043
044    public CombinationQueryPredicate<ClientLoggingQueryBuilderDsl> asCreatedBy(
045            Function<com.commercetools.api.predicates.query.common.CreatedByQueryBuilderDsl, CombinationQueryPredicate<com.commercetools.api.predicates.query.common.CreatedByQueryBuilderDsl>> fn) {
046        return new CombinationQueryPredicate<>(
047            fn.apply(com.commercetools.api.predicates.query.common.CreatedByQueryBuilderDsl.of()),
048            ClientLoggingQueryBuilderDsl::of);
049    }
050
051    public CombinationQueryPredicate<ClientLoggingQueryBuilderDsl> asLastModifiedBy(
052            Function<com.commercetools.api.predicates.query.common.LastModifiedByQueryBuilderDsl, CombinationQueryPredicate<com.commercetools.api.predicates.query.common.LastModifiedByQueryBuilderDsl>> fn) {
053        return new CombinationQueryPredicate<>(
054            fn.apply(com.commercetools.api.predicates.query.common.LastModifiedByQueryBuilderDsl.of()),
055            ClientLoggingQueryBuilderDsl::of);
056    }
057}
